      </p>
      <a class="inline-block text-base lg:text-[1.1rem] font-SourceProBold px-5 py-1.5 bg-tmdbDarkerBlue border-2 border-tmdbDarkerBlue rounded-[20px] uppercase leading-5" href="#">View
